01:11:37,491 --> 01:11:41,362
- 你會好起來的 爸  - 不 不 不是為我自己
- You're gonna be fine, Pop.  - No, no, not for me.

661
01:11:42,162 --> 01:11:46,317
我是害怕會失去你 我讀懂了你的眼神
I'm fearful I'm gonna lose you.I can see what's in your eyes.

662
01:11:51,605 --> 01:11:56,344
- 那你就會知道我要去做什麼  - 你什麼都不需要做
- Then you know what I gotta do.  - You don't have to do anything.

663
01:11:56,444 --> 01:11:59,147
但你我都知道我會做的
But we both know I will.

664
01:12:03,316 --> 01:12:04,919
我去找醫生
I'll get the doc.

665
01:12:05,019 --> 01:12:08,656
約翰·亨利·克萊頓 停下
John Henry Clayton, you stop.

666
01:12:11,058 --> 01:12:13,606
約翰·亨利 拜託
John Henry, please.

667
01:12:19,567 --> 01:12:21,669
拜託
Please...

668
01:12:21,769 --> 01:12:23,839
就當為了我
for me...

669
01:12:25,139 --> 01:12:26,913
別去
don't.

670
01:12:27,013 --> 01:12:29,276
除非有人結束這一切 爸 否則這些事會繼續下去
This ain't gonna end, Pa,till someone ends it.

671
01:12:29,376 --> 01:12:32,847
但不是你 不非得是你啊
Not you. It doesn't have to be you.

672
01:12:33,347 --> 01:12:36,384
我這一生中 該做點兒對的事情了
It's time I did something right in my life.

673
01:12:37,884 --> 01:12:40,291
我知道該怎麼做
This is what I know how to do.

674
01:13:37,411 --> 01:13:40,082
帕森斯先生 這是勒馬特的嗎
Mr. Parsons, is that a LeMat?

675
01:13:40,480 --> 01:13:42,148
是的 先生
Yes, sir.

676
01:13:42,248 --> 01:13:46,553
一個月前 我從一個哥們兒那買來的
I... bought it off a fella about a month ago.

677
01:13:48,622 --> 01:13:51,492
真是個美人兒 不是嗎
She's a real beauty, ain't she?

678
01:13:51,592 --> 01:13:54,729
9發子彈 10口徑的槍管
Nine shots in a 10 gauge shotgun barrel.

679
01:13:54,829 --> 01:13:59,222
給你個公道價
And I can let you have it for a fair price.

680
01:14:00,500 --> 01:14:04,371
或者你可以借走用
Or you can just borrow it.

681
01:15:23,784 --> 01:15:26,521
我想你就是他們口中的"小奈德"
I suspect you're the one they call Little Ned?

682
01:15:34,127 --> 01:15:35,807
是
That's right.

683
01:15:49,842 --> 01:15:54,074
所有今天不想死的人 我建議你們解除武器然後快走
All you young 'uns who ain't willing to die today, I suggest you unarm yourselves and get.

684
01:15:54,174 --> 01:15:56,718
待著別動 小伙子們
Stay where you are, boys.

685
01:16:07,293 --> 01:16:09,797
去你媽的
Goddamn you.

686
01:17:15,598 --> 01:17:17,616
操
Fuck!

687
01:18:24,932 --> 01:18:27,259
口渴了嗎 弗蘭克
Mouth getting dry, Frank?

688
01:18:28,068 --> 01:18:30,906
你是想請我喝一杯嗎
You offering to buy me a drink?

689
01:19:21,921 --> 01:19:24,224
約翰·亨利
John Henry.

690
01:19:34,568 --> 01:19:36,919
不管接下來發生什麼
Whatever happens next,

691
01:19:37,019 --> 01:19:41,558
我需要你知道 我從沒准許過針對你父親的那種懦弱行為
I want you to know I did not sanction that cowardly act against your father.

692
01:19:41,658 --> 01:19:43,375
就我個人來說 我覺得他們的行為實在太該死了
Personally, I found their actions damnable

693
01:19:43,475 --> 01:19:46,181
也活該接受你帶給他們的命運
and deserving of the fate you brought upon them.

694
01:19:46,747 --> 01:19:48,848
然後你會走嗎
Then you'll be leaving?

695
01:19:48,948 --> 01:19:51,184
不能
Can't do that.

696
01:19:51,284 --> 01:19:54,549
沒有人會雇一個遇到麻煩就跑路的槍手
No one hires a gunman who runs from trouble.

697
01:19:56,089 --> 01:19:59,193
你不非得跑 戴夫 你可以用走的
You don't have to run, Dave. You can walk.

698
01:20:01,127 --> 01:20:05,600
我的僱傭條款不會允許我這麼做
The terms of my employment would not allow me to do that.

699
01:20:26,253 --> 01:20:29,747
這把勒馬特可是太沉了 對我很不利啊
This here LeMat's mighty heavy.Puts me at a disadvantage.

700
01:20:31,157 --> 01:20:33,210
你在暗示什麼
What would you suggest?

701
01:20:33,981 --> 01:20:38,285
行個方便 讓我回去拿我的柯爾特如何
Would you be kind enough to let me go back inside and retrieve myself a Colt?

702
01:20:51,244 --> 01:20:53,281
謝謝
Thank you.

703
01:22:28,741 --> 01:22:31,378
我的朋友 你不再受雇於人了
My friend, you are no longer employed.

704
01:22:42,121 --> 01:22:45,191
看起來你是對的
It would appear you are correct.

705
01:22:54,734 --> 01:22:56,737
很高興認識你 戴夫
It's been a pleasure knowing you, Dave.

706
01:23:34,157 --> 01:23:35,599
我很好 爸
I'm all right, Pa.

707
01:23:37,844 --> 01:23:41,296
今天發生的這些事不難解釋
It's not gonna take long for word to get out on what happened here today.

708
01:23:41,396 --> 01:23:44,185
很快就會有外面的人為了出名來找我
Men from far and wide are gonna come looking for me to make a name for themselves.

709
01:23:44,285 --> 01:23:46,518
別走
Don't go away.

710
01:23:46,618 --> 01:23:49,027
我沒辦法自己搞定那片地
I can't finish the field on my own.

711
01:23:49,127 --> 01:23:52,092
我已經都做好了 爸 我已經播種了
The field's finished, Pa. I seeded it.

712
01:23:52,192 --> 01:23:54,761
它會自己好好生長的
It'll take care of itself.

713
01:23:55,361 --> 01:23:57,363
我必須走
I gotta go.

714
01:23:57,463 --> 01:24:00,933
你不會再離開10年吧
You're not going for another 10 years, are you?

715
01:24:01,340 --> 01:24:05,105
不會的 我保證 很快就回來看你 爸
No, I promise. See you soon, Pa.

716
01:24:26,159 --> 01:24:28,629
他之後的生活很少有人知道
<i>Little is known of him after that. </i>

717
01:24:28,729 --> 01:24:30,997
有些人說他去了科菲維爾
<i>Some say he drifted down to Coffeeville</i>

718
01:24:31,097 --> 01:24:34,534
幾年以後 在那兒
<i>where he was involved in another altercation</i>

719
01:24:34,634 --> 01:24:36,470
他又捲入了一場爭端
<i>a few years later.</i>

720
01:24:36,570 --> 01:24:40,472
但是這些指控從未被證實過
<i>But those accusations were never proven.</i>

721
01:24:40,972 --> 01:24:44,478
普遍的觀點認為 他用化名搬到了西邊
<i>The common view was he moved westward under a different name,</i>

722
01:24:44,578 --> 01:24:48,516
在那裏 他孤獨地度過了一生
<i>where he lived a life of quiet isolation.</i>

723
01:24:53,415 --> 01:24:57,239
為人所知的是 幾年之後瑪麗·愛麗絲過世之後
<i>What is known is that when Mary Alice died a few years later,</i>

724
01:24:57,339 --> 01:24:59,993
他沒有出席她的葬禮
<i>he did not attend her funeral.</i>

725
01:25:00,093 --> 01:25:03,764
但是 很多人都說 隔天
<i>However, many say the following day,</i>

726
01:25:03,864 --> 01:25:08,335
她的墓碑上繫著一條褪色的紅絲帶
<i>a faded red ribbon was found attached to her headstone.</i>

727
01:25:16,942 --> 01:25:21,328
多年來 福勒的其他人一直信誓旦旦地說又見到過他
<i>Others in Fowler recounted stories of seeing him throughout the years</i>

728
01:25:21,428 --> 01:25:23,884
直到他父親去世
<i>up until his father's death,</i>

729
01:25:23,984 --> 01:25:28,055
自那之後 他再也沒回來過
<i>at which time he came no more.</i>


